      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA benchmark centrifugal pump — identical geometry to the COU device family. Operating conditions span the full COU envelope. Fluid properties and inlet profiles match COU conditions. Validation scenario is categorized as system-level, directly applicable to the submission COU."
