    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per MRL 2 scoping. Discretization error GCI of 3.1% satisfies the < 5% threshold. Output comparison NIH deviations remain within the ±25% acceptance band across all five operating points. Validation activities are directly relevant to the COU geometry and operating envelope. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
